02:38.358 --> 02:40.760
I vaguely remember it. I went to kindergarten here.

02:40.860 --> 02:41.861
You're right.

02:41.862 --> 02:44.064
Shinshuu (Nagano area) is also your home.

02:44.164 --> 02:45.198
It's dad's too.

02:45.199 --> 02:46.503
