03:18.698 --> 03:21.201
Is that the cell phone strap your dad bought for you?

03:21.401 --> 03:25.038
What, does it hurt your feelings that I'm still keeping it?

03:25.238 --> 03:27.209
As if I get hurt so easily!

03:27.238 --> 03:29.009
- Really?
- Really.

03:29.209 --> 03:30.911
I'm hungry.

03:31.011 --> 03:33.413
You just ate lunch when we transferred in Nagoya.

03:33.513 --> 03:35.015
A boy in puberty

03:35.215 --> 03:37.217
