03:37.317 --> 03:41.519
I wish a mother of a boy in his growth spurt would at least know that!

03:42.021 --> 03:44.014
Who do you think you're talking to?

03:49.000 --> 03:52.200
<i>Shinshuu, City of Nagano</i>

03:52.500 --> 03:55.993
