04:27.300 --> 04:31.293
I will now introduce you to a new classmate.

04:32.305 --> 04:36.998
He's Saitou Kazuo.

04:38.278 --> 04:42.281
Saitou moved here from Onomichi, Hiroshima Prefecture.

04:42.282 --> 04:44.283
