06:01.361 --> 06:04.397
You haven't kissed me since.

06:04.697 --> 06:06.299
Kazumi!

06:06.399 --> 06:09.602
You kissed Saitou while sleeping with him?

06:09.702 --> 06:11.603
He kissed you and wet his bed...

06:11.604 --> 06:13.473
<i>then</i> what did you two do?

06:13.673 --> 06:14.672
We had a nap.

06:14.673 --> 06:16.375
His underwear was wet,

06:16.376 --> 06:19.378
