09:26.566 --> 09:29.570
That you killed my grandma.

09:30.470 --> 09:31.672
Huh?

09:32.572 --> 09:36.575
<i>Once upon a time, Kazuo and Kazumi came home from kindergarten,</i>

09:36.576 --> 09:39.580
<i>and saw a fly entering grandma's mouth.</i>

09:42.180 --> 09:48.584
<i>Incredibly, Kazuo suddenly started spraying insecticide into grandma's mouth!</i>

09:50.100 --> 09:53.604
<i>Pshhh, pshhh!</i>

09:57.000 --> 10:02.403
