21:04.263 --> 21:05.965
We're not kids.

21:06.050 --> 21:07.752
Whether it's dream or reality,

21:07.767 --> 21:10.060
let's just think it through.

21:18.800 --> 21:20.402
My home is this way.

21:21.080 --> 21:22.483
What are we going to do?

21:22.580 --> 21:24.183
Let's discuss it inside.

21:24.283 --> 21:26.676
We've got to do something about this.

21:29.588 --> 21:32.191
Where have you been hiding for so long?

21:32.291 --> 21:33.892
It's not like that, mom.

21:33.893 --> 21:36.094
This is Kazumi, and I'm Kazuo!

21:36.095 --> 21:38.097
This girl is still not making any sense.

21:38.098 --> 21:41.101
Stop trying to seduce my Kazuo!

21:41.301 --> 21:43.303
What's wrong, Kazuo?

21:44.003 --> 21:46.105
No! This is Kazumi!

21:46.305 --> 21:49.308
I'm sorry, Kazumi. Please leave for today.

21:49.408 --> 21:51.101
Hang in there!

22:03.522 --> 22:05.226
This is yours, isn't it?

22:07.026 --> 22:08.719
Go home already!

22:28.748 --> 22:31.650
Excuse me... I mean, I'm home.

22:35.855 --> 22:37.548
Thank you for waiting.

22:40.260 --> 22:41.762
Where have you been?

22:41.862 --> 22:44.463
I told you to enter from the back during this time.

22:44.464 --> 22:46.466
We have customers here!

22:47.466 --> 22:49.469
Hurry and eat dinner.

22:50.369 --> 22:54.062
Why did you bring back the dipper?

22:54.674 --> 22:57.676
Tell grandpa to take this back tomorrow.

22:57.776 --> 22:58.779
OK.

23:00.279 --> 23:02.472
- Welcome home.
- Thanks.

23:17.196 --> 23:18.498
Auntie ate mine!

23:18.596 --> 23:19.797
Call me sis.

23:19.798 --> 23:22.200
I'm the only child.

23:22.201 --> 23:24.204
You don't even like oyster mushrooms.

23:24.904 --> 23:26.405
It's first come, first serve today!

23:26.406 --> 23:28.108
Kazumi, get me the rice.

23:28.208 --> 23:30.410
Your mom is busy cleaning up the restaurant.

23:30.510 --> 23:31.803
Fine...

23:41.220 --> 23:42.713
Another bowl!

24:28.400 --> 24:30.202
What's wrong, Kazumi?

24:30.302 --> 24:31.671
No appetite today?

24:31.871 --> 24:33.274
No...

24:34.674 --> 24:36.467
Her stomach is growling!

24:58.497 --> 25:00.499
I finally finished cleaning up!

25:00.599 --> 25:02.401
Kazumi...

25:02.501 --> 25:04.402
I'm glad you can eat oyster mushrooms, but...

25:04.403 --> 25:08.105
you're a girl! Where are your manners?

25:08.106 --> 25:09.808
Go back to your own seat.

25:10.008 --> 25:11.410
That way, auntie!

25:11.510 --> 25:12.611
Come on...

25:12.612 --> 25:13.614
Sake...

25:16.214 --> 25:17.807
For me too.

25:33.231 --> 25:34.833
I'm home!

25:35.933 --> 25:38.735
I talked to our landlord after greeting the neighbors.

25:38.736 --> 25:42.629
She happens to be a quite a talker!
I ended up having a long chat with her.

25:43.542 --> 25:45.543
This bar used to be very popular in the past,

25:45.544 --> 25:50.148
but they got beaten by new competition nearby.

25:50.550 --> 25:55.254
"An old woman like me can't keep up with the trends",
she said with a smile.

25:55.554 --> 25:57.556
Look, she gave me some persimmon!

25:57.956 --> 25:59.958
Sorry I'm late, you must be hungry.

26:00.558 --> 26:02.561
Should we just order some noodles?

26:03.961 --> 26:05.564
Where did you get this?

26:05.864 --> 26:07.466
I made it.

26:07.566 --> 26:09.859
<i>You</i> did? By yourself?

26:12.671 --> 26:13.964
Yes.

26:14.171 --> 26:16.864
Feeling depressed will only make me even sadder.

26:17.576 --> 26:20.578
Sorry for using the food without asking you.

26:20.579 --> 26:23.582
What? You always take the food without asking!

26:23.682 --> 26:27.884
I asked the landlord to leave her old appliances here.

26:27.986 --> 26:30.389
Oh, yes... right.

26:30.589 --> 26:32.791
By the way, what do you have to be depressed about?

26:32.891 --> 26:34.892
About Akemi?

26:34.893 --> 26:36.595
Or that weird Kazumi?

26:36.695 --> 26:38.499
Who's Akemi?

26:40.799 --> 26:42.803
You miss her after all!

26:44.703 --> 26:48.505
You must be doing all this because you're worried about me.

26:48.607 --> 26:52.211
No, I'm just trying to imitate other people's cooking.

26:52.411 --> 26:56.404
Really? But sometimes it tastes horrible when you do that!

26:59.818 --> 27:01.520
Wow, it tastes great!

27:01.620 --> 27:03.621
What's gotten into you, Kazuo?

27:03.622 --> 27:05.424
- Is it good?
- Yes!

27:05.524 --> 27:06.926
Then I'm relieved.

27:07.226 --> 27:09.428
- By the way...
- Yes?

27:09.528 --> 27:11.629
Daddy... I mean,

27:11.630 --> 27:13.532
When's dad coming home?

27:13.632 --> 27:17.536
Kazuo, are you still saying that to hurt my feelings?

27:17.636 --> 27:21.040
No, um, err...

27:21.540 --> 27:24.543
You're being so difficult lately.

27:24.643 --> 27:27.579
You even brought some weird girl home.

27:27.679 --> 27:29.680
All this stress...

27:29.681 --> 27:32.374
it's a great diet!

27:35.687 --> 27:39.391
Let's eat. I'm happy my son cooked for me.

27:39.491 --> 27:42.284
Thank you for the meal.
- Thank you for the meal.

27:46.698 --> 27:48.391
Ah, TV!

27:55.073 --> 27:57.074
What are you doing, I turned it on.

27:57.075 --> 27:59.777
This is my TV time.

27:59.778 --> 28:01.580
I don't care.

28:01.880 --> 28:04.782
Kazumi, it's not your turn.

28:04.783 --> 28:08.576
You guys actually have a rule like that?
- What's gotten into you?

28:09.788 --> 28:11.189
Never mind.

28:14.793 --> 28:17.496
Don't worry, I'll do the dishes.

28:17.996 --> 28:21.498
Hey, Kazuo, you can watch the bar's TV.

28:21.700 --> 28:22.702
TV?

28:22.802 --> 28:25.704
What's it called? That classical music show you watch every week.

28:25.804 --> 28:28.706
You know, the one you used to watch with Akemi.

28:28.707 --> 28:32.311
She must be the reason you started learning piano.

28:32.711 --> 28:34.712
Akemi is good at everything,

28:34.713 --> 28:37.715
good mannered. I really liked her.

28:37.716 --> 28:41.709
I hope you'll make a friend like her in this school too.

28:43.722 --> 28:46.724
Right... but I'll clean these.

28:46.725 --> 28:50.718
Oh? But you don't have to worry about me.

28:51.730 --> 28:55.234
Doing something is better than nothing.

28:55.734 --> 28:58.537
Actually, I need to use the bathroom first...

28:58.737 --> 29:01.440
Huh? You don't have to ask me.

29:01.740 --> 29:03.143
Oh, right.

29:04.643 --> 29:06.645
Well then...

29:06.745 --> 29:09.747
Don't read books in there!

29:09.748 --> 29:11.750
I'm using it soon too.

29:11.950 --> 29:16.952
Geez, where did he pick up that strange habit?

29:19.758 --> 29:22.760
"The Sickness Unto Death"?

29:22.761 --> 29:25.763
"Kierkegaard", what a weird name.

29:25.764 --> 29:29.166
I thought this would relax me, but it's the complete opposite!

29:29.167 --> 29:30.801
Auntie, are you done yet?

29:30.802 --> 29:33.804
Kazumi, how long are you going to be in there?

29:33.805 --> 29:35.408
Diarrhea?

29:36.908 --> 29:38.776
What's that?

29:38.777 --> 29:40.778
What's with you?

29:40.779 --> 29:43.781
When did you start reading books in the bathroom?

29:43.782 --> 29:45.783
When? I have for a long time...

29:45.784 --> 29:48.785
Whatever, hurry and use it.

29:48.786 --> 29:50.789
I'm also waiting for the bathroom.

29:51.189 --> 29:53.182
Kazumi, show me that book.

29:55.594 --> 29:57.787
I'll go after you.
- You can go before me...

30:00.799 --> 30:02.701
Where's the phone?

30:02.801 --> 30:04.802
What's wrong with you, Kazuo?

30:04.803 --> 30:06.596
The phone is over there.

30:12.310 --> 30:15.114
He's strange tonight.

30:16.714 --> 30:18.717
Why are you just sitting there, Kazumi?

30:18.817 --> 30:20.818
Hurry and clean up, then make tea for everyone.

30:20.819 --> 30:23.622
And what's with this disturbing book?

30:23.822 --> 30:25.823
Something Unto Death?

30:25.824 --> 30:27.025
I have to make tea?

30:27.026 --> 30:29.728
Of course! And what's with the boy talk?

30:29.828 --> 30:32.830
(Girl Talk:) I have to make tea?
- Yes.

30:32.831 --> 30:35.734
Don't worry about the tea, get the phone.

30:35.834 --> 30:38.337
Damn, what a busy house.

30:38.837 --> 30:41.038
What are you doing? Get the phone!

30:41.039 --> 30:42.741
Right, phone...

30:42.841 --> 30:45.444
She must have bumped her head too.

30:45.544 --> 30:47.537
I'll make tea!

30:54.853 --> 30:57.846
Where's the phone...

30:59.858 --> 31:02.261
Oh, here it is.

31:03.361 --> 31:04.663
Hello?

31:04.763 --> 31:06.765
It's me, Kazumi.

31:06.865 --> 31:08.866
I know that, it's my own voice.

31:08.867 --> 31:11.270
Kazuo, there's an emergency with your body.

31:11.370 --> 31:12.373
Emergency?

31:12.473 --> 31:15.576
The shape... suddenly changed!

31:15.676 --> 31:17.078
Shape? What shape?

31:17.176 --> 31:18.578
Where you pee from...

31:18.678 --> 31:21.081
Idiot! Don't play with that!

31:21.178 --> 31:24.781
But... I only wiped it with toilet paper after going...

31:24.883 --> 31:26.884
It started to change shape.

31:26.885 --> 31:28.886
Idiot, who wipes that with paper?

31:28.887 --> 31:33.180
Just swing it a couple of times and put it back in!

31:33.892 --> 31:35.594
Don't do funny stuff to it!

31:35.694 --> 31:37.398
I got it.

31:39.798 --> 31:42.601
But <i>you</i> have to use the paper.

31:42.701 --> 31:44.104
Fine.

31:44.204 --> 31:46.907
Hey, how's it going at your end?

31:47.000 --> 31:48.803
Ain't so bad, I guess.

31:48.907 --> 31:51.408
You can't talk like that!

31:51.409 --> 31:52.910
Anyway, what about you?

31:52.911 --> 31:54.115
Everything going well?

31:54.311 --> 31:56.815
I cooked something, and we ate together, but...

31:56.915 --> 32:01.117
your mom seemed to be surprised at how fast I ate.

32:01.118 --> 32:01.919
Really...

32:01.920 --> 32:04.923
You know how I have a big family.

32:05.423 --> 32:07.416
If you don't eat quickly...

32:09.923 --> 32:11.816
There will be none left.

32:11.930 --> 32:15.932
I know what you mean. It took a while to grab the food.

32:15.934 --> 32:18.938
You have to eat properly

32:19.938 --> 32:22.072
It's my body.

32:22.073 --> 32:23.941
But I'm a bit relieved.

32:23.942 --> 32:27.944
You're calm enough to cook.

32:27.946 --> 32:30.949
I'll try to think of something about our situation.

32:31.249 --> 32:34.051
- That and...
- Yes?

32:34.151 --> 32:36.354
Did you see a cell phone in my pocket?

32:36.454 --> 32:37.955
There was.

32:37.956 --> 32:41.659
But it's all wet, so the memory is all gone.

32:41.660 --> 32:42.461
It doesn't matter.

32:42.462 --> 32:44.498
But the strap...

32:45.998 --> 32:48.966
Oh, this? The piano-shaped one?

32:48.967 --> 32:50.402
Can you keep it somewhere safe?

32:50.502 --> 32:52.504
Is it a gift from someone important?

32:52.804 --> 32:54.073
This Akemi person?

32:54.173 --> 32:57.576
No, it's from my pops.

32:57.676 --> 32:59.078
From your father?

32:59.278 --> 33:01.880
Well then, I'm going to hang up.
Take care.

33:01.980 --> 33:03.682
You too.

33:03.782 --> 33:05.075
Bye.

33:10.088 --> 33:11.691
What, again?

33:12.991 --> 33:15.694
What, you still have something to say?

33:16.194 --> 33:18.797
It's Kazumi... right?

33:18.997 --> 33:20.998
Oh, ah... Yes.

33:20.999 --> 33:23.434
It's me, Hiroshi.

33:23.435 --> 33:25.237
Oh, Hiroshi is that...

33:25.238 --> 33:28.907
class president, Kazumi's boyfriend, show-off, Yamamoto Hiroshi?

33:29.007 --> 33:31.410
What's the matter? You're acting strange today, Kazumi.

33:31.510 --> 33:34.011
I'm not acting strange, damn it.

33:34.012 --> 33:35.414
(Girl Talk:) I mean... I'm not strange.

33:35.514 --> 33:37.013
There's definitely something wrong.

33:37.014 --> 33:40.017
I called your cell phone many times, but it wouldn't connect, so I called your home.

33:40.019 --> 33:43.020
Oh, my cell... It's in my home...

33:43.021 --> 33:44.023
Huh?

33:44.723 --> 33:46.825
(Girl talk:) It was soaked in water.

33:46.925 --> 33:49.928
Soaked?
- I went to the Spring of Sabishira.

33:50.028 --> 33:53.030
You know, I took the transfer student, Kazuo there.

33:53.031 --> 33:55.734
Then I fell in the water.

33:55.934 --> 33:57.936
Really? I hope you're not hurt.

33:58.036 --> 34:00.037
Duh, that's why I'm home.

34:00.038 --> 34:03.040
Right... I don't mean to be rude,

34:03.041 --> 34:05.944
but is this another one of your stories?

34:06.044 --> 34:08.045
Huh, uh, um...

34:08.045 --> 34:10.047
(Unnatural girl Talk:) This is truth it is.

34:10.047 --> 34:13.050
(Girl Talk:) Kazuo is very strong.

34:13.051 --> 34:15.054
(Girl Talk:) He saved me.

34:16.054 --> 34:18.056
Something's definitely wrong.

34:18.056 --> 34:19.558
I'm coming over right now.

34:19.559 --> 34:21.058
No, no, don't come!

34:21.059 --> 34:23.260
- Please don't come!
- But...

34:23.261 --> 34:25.062
Don't worry, I'm just tired.

34:25.063 --> 34:28.065
Maybe that's why I'm a bit nervous.

34:28.065 --> 34:31.168
So you don't need to come tonight.

34:31.168 --> 34:33.170
I see...

34:33.170 --> 34:35.175
Then... rest well.

34:36.175 --> 34:38.676
Do you think you can come to school tomorrow?

34:38.677 --> 34:39.978
I think so.

34:39.978 --> 34:41.972
Bye, good night.

34:59.097 --> 35:00.598
Who was it?

35:00.599 --> 35:02.201
Such a long call.

35:03.001 --> 35:05.003
It was Hiroshi.

35:05.103 --> 35:08.106
You've had a long day, go to sleep.

35:09.106 --> 35:12.109
Don't forget to greet grandma before going to sleep.

35:12.110 --> 35:14.913
Ask her to heal your head.

35:15.113 --> 35:17.115
Grandma's still alive?

35:17.215 --> 35:20.018
What is she talking about?

35:20.118 --> 35:22.111
That's a tough book.

35:25.323 --> 35:27.816
Tie your sash properly!

35:30.128 --> 35:32.131
This way, go.

35:33.331 --> 35:37.324
Pray that you'll feel better tomorrow.

35:38.536 --> 35:40.939
I'm sleeping here?!

35:41.039 --> 35:44.042
What? You have your own room.

35:44.242 --> 35:46.845
Now, give her a greeting.

35:48.145 --> 35:51.645
( Random chanting... )

35:54.352 --> 35:57.055
Kazuo, are you asleep?

35:57.155 --> 36:00.158
No, what is it?

36:00.558 --> 36:04.195
I ironed your uniform.

36:04.295 --> 36:06.064
Oh, thanks!

36:06.164 --> 36:10.157
I'll also iron that weird Kazumi's uniform.

36:12.270 --> 36:15.073
I found her cell phone too, but it's broken.

36:15.173 --> 36:17.275
But return it tomorrow.

36:17.375 --> 36:19.878
Who knows how that crazy girl will react?

36:20.178 --> 36:23.282
Really, I can't believe she turned out to be such an annoying kid.

36:24.082 --> 36:26.075
Ah! Hot, hot, hot!

36:59.818 --> 37:00.819
Kazuo.

37:00.900 --> 37:02.637
Oh, you're here?

37:05.456 --> 37:09.158
Are you crazy? You can't wear that to school.

37:09.260 --> 37:11.261
I've brought your uniform.

37:11.262 --> 37:13.263
Your mom washed it for you.

37:13.264 --> 37:16.935
Here's your precious cell phone strap,

37:17.035 --> 37:18.537
and my broken cell phone.

37:18.737 --> 37:21.740
I can't get the buttons on!

37:22.240 --> 37:24.843
What are you doing? Wear a bra underneath!

37:24.943 --> 37:26.445
People can see my breasts!

37:26.545 --> 37:27.547
Calm down.

37:27.645 --> 37:30.147
Over there, in the top drawer.

37:36.254 --> 37:38.847
What's that?
- Don't touch that!

37:44.762 --> 37:46.355
Help me with this.

37:49.267 --> 37:50.768
Good morning, Kazumi.

37:50.769 --> 37:52.771
How are you feeling?

37:53.071 --> 37:55.073
You? What are you doing?

37:55.173 --> 37:58.476
Mom, I always tell you to knock before entering my room!

37:58.876 --> 38:01.079
What about you?

38:01.179 --> 38:03.281
Entering a girl's room this early in the morning?

38:03.381 --> 38:07.285
Uh, I came to bring his cell phone strap and uniform.

38:07.385 --> 38:11.184
She came because she was worried I suddenly turned into a girl.

38:11.185 --> 38:12.687
You don't have to get all mad.

38:12.791 --> 38:14.893
Who do you think you're talking to?

38:15.093 --> 38:17.697
And why aren't you wearing anything?

38:19.197 --> 38:22.200
What did you do that for, old lady?!
- Kazuo, stop!

38:22.300 --> 38:24.303
What did you just call me?

38:25.303 --> 38:28.304
Why are you here in my daughter's room?

38:28.305 --> 38:30.309
Do you think this is appropriate?

38:31.309 --> 38:33.344
Honey!

38:33.444 --> 38:35.915
This is inappropriate too!

38:39.017 --> 38:41.119
What's going on?!

38:41.419 --> 38:43.421
Your skirt is on backwards.

38:43.521 --> 38:45.724
Oops.

38:48.426 --> 38:51.630
Are the folks in your home going to be alright?

38:52.230 --> 38:55.234
They're fine. It happens all the time.

38:56.034 --> 38:57.037
Oh.

38:59.237 --> 39:02.941
You may be good at these things,

39:03.041 --> 39:08.043
but I'm not used to living in an unrealistic situation like this.

39:10.348 --> 39:12.350
What's wrong?

39:12.450 --> 39:16.254
I'm starting to want to kill myself.

39:16.354 --> 39:18.356
Whoa, don't be absurd!

39:18.357 --> 39:21.058
What will happen to me if you died?

39:21.059 --> 39:24.063
Your body belongs to me.

39:24.563 --> 39:26.565
I know that.

39:27.265 --> 39:29.267
Good morning.

39:29.367 --> 39:31.368
Let's just go to the school.

39:31.369 --> 39:35.170
Good morning.

39:35.171 --> 39:36.572
(Girl Talk:) Let's go.

39:36.573 --> 39:37.574
(Girl Talk:) Yes.

39:37.575 --> 39:39.276
(Boy Talk:) I mean, Yes.

39:39.277 --> 39:40.879
Is that correct?

39:41.079 --> 39:43.079
Ah! I missed breakfast!

39:43.479 --> 39:44.883
I'm hungry.

39:51.000 --> 39:53.793
- Kazumi and...
- Kazuo!

39:56.294 --> 39:58.296
All rise,

39:58.396 --> 40:00.397
bow.

40:00.398 --> 40:02.399
Good morning.

40:02.400 --> 40:03.404
Morning!

40:03.500 --> 40:05.104
Sit down.

40:06.404 --> 40:09.406
For today's music lesson...

40:09.407 --> 40:12.409
Let's enjoy...

40:12.410 --> 40:15.013
a piano performance first!

40:15.413 --> 40:17.406
Yay!

40:22.720 --> 40:24.322
Saitou.

40:24.422 --> 40:26.423
Yes.

40:26.424 --> 40:29.426
Oh, I wasn't calling you, Kazumi.

40:29.427 --> 40:32.230
It's Saitou Kazuo.

40:32.430 --> 40:34.665
Saitou Kazuo actually happens to be

40:34.666 --> 40:37.937
a great piano player from Onomichi.

40:39.437 --> 40:41.441
Isn't that right?

40:42.741 --> 40:44.742
Don't be shy.

40:44.743 --> 40:48.736
Well then, Kazuo. Go ahead.

40:59.190 --> 41:00.992
Come on, Kazuo.

41:01.092 --> 41:02.694
The piano is waiting for you.

41:03.794 --> 41:07.787
Kazuo, you can do it!

41:13.405 --> 41:15.407
What's wrong, Kazuo?

41:15.507 --> 41:18.510
You're good at piano, right?

41:18.810 --> 41:23.312
Come on, Kazuo. Like a hero from Kazumi's fairy tale...

41:23.482 --> 41:27.175
Play the piano like a prince!

41:29.487 --> 41:31.488
(Boy Talk:) What are you doing?

41:31.489 --> 41:34.893
Just spread your fingers, hit the keys and it'll make sound!

41:35.093 --> 41:39.097
Do-re-mi or Flea Waltz, or whatever, just play you idiot!

41:39.497 --> 41:41.098
(Girl Talk:) How can you expect me

41:41.099 --> 41:43.100
to actually play the piano all of a sudden?

41:43.101 --> 41:44.803
This is all your fault

41:45.003 --> 41:48.039
for learning piano without telling me.
Idiot!

41:50.339 --> 41:51.508
Oh, crap!

41:51.509 --> 41:53.011
Kazuo!

41:53.111 --> 41:56.113
Time-out for a sec.
Kazumi, wait! Don't kill yourself!

42:01.720 --> 42:03.723
Watch over the class.

