50:44.076 --> 50:47.077
What do you say, Kazumi?
Want to make some soba again?

50:47.078 --> 50:47.777
Honey?

50:47.778 --> 50:49.978
Soba? Kazumi can make soba?

50:50.080 --> 50:53.082
