53:03.180 --> 53:04.781
Are you practicing for the school play?

53:04.782 --> 53:08.785
Kouichi, Kouichi! She made soba with her feet!

53:09.000 --> 53:10.302
With her feet?!

53:10.387 --> 53:11.689
