53:23.886 --> 53:24.889
Huh?

53:24.989 --> 53:26.694
That's a great thing.

53:26.794 --> 53:30.433
I wasn't interested in making soba,
so I ran off to Tokyo, but

53:30.434 --> 53:32.437
