53:32.438 --> 53:35.444
You might even become a pioneer of female soba masters.

53:35.445 --> 53:40.419
To achieve your goal... do whatever you need to, even with your feet!

53:41.323 --> 53:43.227
You have my support.
- Kouichi...

53:43.327 --> 53:44.330
Honey!

53:44.428 --> 53:45.231
OK.

53:45.431 --> 53:48.137
You're pretty understanding, bro!

53:48.237 --> 53:49.741
Understanding!

53:49.941 --> 53:52.445
